{"tid":2212072,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[薄扶林大學] 我條女無啦啦話聽日1230要去搵happy伯 係咪帽左","createTime":"2020-09-21T13:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T01:45:50.000Z","uid":269515,"like":59,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"419f994554f123ee62584a62e873fe6a42629df9","tid":2212072,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"原來我聽錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係1230去Happy Park<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7L3Wy7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7L3Wy7.jpg&h=aac80ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家聽日開學日<br />\n一齊幫手痴返個連儂牆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時仲有學生組織派明信片同搞活動<br />\n<br />\n詳情睇返依到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSG3b6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSG3b6J.jpg&h=7a037a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFUe9ZNhPFg/?igshid=kuvvirocx7j4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFUe9ZNhPFg%2F%3Figshid%3Dkuvvirocx7j4&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=97aa611f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFUe9ZNhPFg%2F%3Figshid%3Dkuvvirocx7j4&h=bfb3db34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFUe9ZNhPFg/?igshid=kuvvirocx7j4</a><br />\n<br />\n落堂就去寫<br />\n無藉口話遠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12位被送中手足有一位係港大學生<br />\n有時諗起返學嘅時候可能同佢擦身而過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">大家聽日見</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">唔想做黨大/中